  "remarks": "Senior member of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Recruited for ISIL and instructed individuals to perpetrate terrorist acts via online video. Physical description: height: 156cm; weight: 60 kg (as at Sep. 2016); eye colour: black; hair colour: black; build: medium; high cheekbones. Speaks Tagalog, English, Arabic.  \nReview pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023. \n INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
